# Changelog

## [2.3.1] - 2026-03-25

### Fixed
- Wait action timeout is now configurable using the `globalSelectorTimeoutMs` config parameter.

## [2.3.0] - 2026-03-17

### Added
- Per-page watchdog timeout (`pageTimeoutMs`, default 5 minutes) to avoid hanging indefinitely.
- Non-verbose per-page progress logs with elapsed time.

### Changed
- HTML extra content is now provided as an inline string via `--html-extra` (file-based option removed).
- `withTimeout` helper moved to shared utils.

### Fixed
- Prevented unnecessary waiting when a free browser is already in the pool.

## [2.2.1] - 2026-03-13

### Added
- Per-crawl include/exclude path patterns (`includePathPattern`, `excludePathPattern`) to filter discovered URLs.

## [2.2.0] - 2026-03-12

### Added
- Configurable report mode (`reportMode`) to control whether all pages, only changed pages, or changed-first output is printed.
- Configurable diff image saving (`saveDiffs`) to control when diff images are written.
- Configurable retry count (`retryFailedPages`) for re-running failed page tests.

### Changed
- Page results output now supports changed-first reporting and respects the configured diff threshold when listing changed pages.

## [2.1.1] - 2026-03-11

### Changed
- Clicking now forces interaction even when elements are not visible to improve reliability.

## [2.1.0] - 2026-03-01

### Changed
- Output messages are now clearer.

## [2.0.0] - 2026-02-28

### Added
- Page crawling implementation.
- Run-and-email automation script.
- Verbose logging mode for execution tracing.

### Changed
- Screenshot capture stability improved with viewport fixes, timeout waits, and better animation handling.
- Root URL handling corrected.

### Fixed
- General error handling improvements and better runtime diagnostics.
- Console output cleanup (removed debug/noisy logs, added clearer info/error logs).

## [1.1.0] - 2026-02-27

### Added
- Baseline update status message output.
- Custom browser executable configuration, including `firefox-esr` support.
- Configurable config file path.
- Configurable timeouts for browser and screenshot operations.

## [1.0.0] - 2024-09-12

### Added
- First release.
